    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the burger[s] have had 20 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and flip the <strong>burger patty[ies] </strong>over</p><p>Add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon </strong>to the other side of the tray[s] and drizzle over <strong>half</strong> your <strong>BBQ sauce</strong> (you’ll use the rest later!)</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 10 min or until the bacon is starting to crisp and the burger is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>burger and BBQ glazed bacon</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
