    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the burger and BBQ glazed bacon<strong> </strong>is ready, remove the tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Top the burger[s] with the <strong>sliced cheddar</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>remaining BBQ sauce</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>brioche bun[s] </strong>to the tray[s] and return to the oven for a final 2 min or until the cheese has melted and the bun is warmed through</p>",
