    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>brioche base</strong> with a <strong>lettuce leaf</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>cheesy BBQ burger</strong> followed by the <strong>BBQ glazed bacon </strong>and<strong> </strong>a few <strong>onion rings </strong>and top with a <strong>warmed brioche lid</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>dressed salad </strong>and <strong>chips</strong> to the side with any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>onion rings</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
